<item>
            <title>[PIG-2821] HBaseStorage should work with secure hbase</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2821</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;HBaseStorage needs to add HBase delegation token to the Job object if hbase security is enabled.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12599148">PIG-2821</key>
            <summary>HBaseStorage should work with secure hbase</summary>
